  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00284', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-113-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '因應全球氣候變遷及節能減碳政策方向，臺灣近年積極推動執行綠色金
