  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00285', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-113-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '某公司參與商場標租案進行財務試算：本案依招標文件屬五年定期租賃
